         <div id="c15446" class="csc-default">
          <div class="direct-style" style="height:350px;">
           <div class="csc-header csc-header-n1">
            <h2>ABOUT THE CONFERENCE</h2>
           </div>
           <p class="bodytext">CTBT: Science and Technology 2013 Conference (SnT2013) was the fourth in a series of conferences that help establish interactions and partnerships between the scientific and technological community and the <a href="specials/who-we-are/" title="Opens internal link in current window" target="_self" class="internal-link">CTBTO</a>. Scientists made over 80 oral presentations and <a href="fileadmin/user_upload/SnT2013/SnT_Conference_Full_Programme.pdf" title="Initiates file download" class="download">over 250 poster presentations</a> at the conference to more than 750 conference participants.&nbsp; </p> 
           <p class="bodytext">Read the <a href="http://clv108.ctbto.org/index.php?id=4057" title="Opens external link in new window" target="_blank" class="external-link-new-window">introduction</a> to the conference by <a href="the-organization/the-provisional-technical-secretariat-pts/organizational-structure-of-the-pts/curriculum-vitaelassina-zerboexecutive-secretary/" title="Opens internal link in current window" target="_self" class="internal-link">Lassina Zerbo</a>, SnT2013 Project Executive and Executive Secretary-elect. </p> 
           <p class="bodytext">Read the <a href="press-centre/highlights/2013/the-science-and-technology-conference-2013/" title="Opens internal link in current window" target="_self" class="internal-link">highlight</a> (26 June) on the conference. </p> 
           <p class="bodytext">&nbsp;</p> 
           <p class="bodytext">This conference was made possible by the generous contribution of the Austrian Federal Ministry for European and International Affairs. </p>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
