           <div class="csc-header csc-header-n5">
            <h2>THEMES</h2>
           </div>
           <p class="bodytext"> The conference covered three themes: </p> 
           <p class="bodytext">1. <a href="specials/snt2013/theme-1-the-earth-as-a-complex-system/" title="Opens internal link in current window" target="_self" class="internal-link">The Earth as a complex system</a> </p> 
           <p class="bodytext">2. <a href="specials/snt2013/theme-2-events-and-their-characterization/" title="Opens internal link in current window" target="_self" class="internal-link">Events and their characterization</a> </p> 
           <p class="bodytext">3. <a href="specials/snt2013/theme-3-advances-in-sensors-networks-and-processing/" title="Opens internal link in current window" target="_self" class="internal-link">Advances in sensors, networks and processing</a> </p> 
           <p class="bodytext">&nbsp;</p>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color:#A5BBBA;padding-bottom:1px;background-image:url(uploads/tx_sbcontbg/bg_color_grey_status.gif);background-repeat:repeat-x;" class="">
         <div id="c15432" class="csc-default">
          <div class="direct-style" style="height:190px;">
