            <li><a href="http://news.oneindia.in/feature/2013/vienna-international-scientific-conference-on-ctbt-1246641.html" title="Opens external link in new window" target="_blank" class="external-link-new-window">'India might have to eat its own words on CTBT', by George Chakko (OneIndia)</a></li>
           </ul>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color:#EBA535;padding-bottom:1px;background-image:url(uploads/tx_sbcontbg/bg_color_orange_feature.gif);background-repeat:repeat-x;" class="">
         <div id="c15442" class="csc-default">
          <div class="direct-style" style="height:224px;">
           <div class="csc-header csc-header-n5">
            <h2>Conference Goals</h2>
           </div>
           <ul>
            <li>Capitalize on scientific and technological innovations for verifying CTBT compliance</li>
            <li>Promote the wider scientific application of data that are used for test-ban verification</li>
            <li>Enhance the exchange of knowledge and ideas between the CTBTO and the broader scientific community</li>
            <li>Enlarge the scientific community engaged in test-ban monitoring</li>
           </ul>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
